---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Submission Guidelines | Nahor">
  <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 0 20px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; text-align: justify;">
    
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 42px; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #1A1A1A; text-align: center; letter-spacing: -1px;">
      Submission Guidelines
    </h1>
    
    <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 28px; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1A1A1A;">Submission Philosophy</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Nahor is a curated digital publication. Every submission is welcomed and thoughtfully considered. However, publication is not automatic. Our editorial team reviews submissions based on originality, quality, clarity, and suitability for the magazine.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 40px;">The objective is to build a long-term archive of meaningful creative work while respecting every contributor's ownership of their work.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 28px; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1A1A1A;">Submission Terms</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Before submitting, contributors should agree to the following:</p>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">Originality</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">The contributor confirms that:</p>
    <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The submitted work is their own original creation.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The work does not infringe upon another person's copyright or intellectual property.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">They have the legal right to submit the work.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">Copyright</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">The contributor <strong>retains full copyright</strong> to their work. Nahor does <strong>not</strong> claim ownership of submitted works.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Instead, if the work is accepted, the contributor grants Nahor a <strong>non-exclusive license</strong> to:</p>
    <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Publish the work on the Nahor website.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Display the work within current and future Issues.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Archive the work permanently.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Promote the published work through Nahor's official platforms while giving appropriate credit to the author.</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Because the license is non-exclusive:</p>
    <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The contributor remains the copyright holder.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The contributor may later publish the work elsewhere, include it in books, portfolios, or personal websites, subject to any acknowledgment policy Nahor may adopt in the future.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">Editorial Process</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Every submission is reviewed by the editorial team. Contributors can expect a response within a few weeks of submission. Editors may suggest:</p>
    <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Grammatical corrections</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Formatting improvements</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Minor editorial refinements</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Substantial edits should be discussed with the contributor before publication. Submission does <strong>not</strong> guarantee publication.</p>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">AI Policy</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Nahor values original human creativity. AI-assisted editing or proofreading may be acceptable, but submissions should primarily reflect the contributor's own creative work, ideas, and expression.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 32px;">For science and technology submissions, the use of AI tools for data processing or coding should be transparently disclosed. This policy can evolve as Nahor grows.</p>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">Photography & Artwork</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">For visual submissions, contributors confirm that:</p>
    <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">They created the artwork or photograph themselves, or</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">They possess the necessary rights to authorize its publication.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">Plagiarism</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Nahor does not publish plagiarized content. If plagiarism or copyright infringement is discovered before or after publication, the editorial team reserves the right to reject or remove the work.</p>

    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600;">Privacy</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Contributor information such as name, email, and uploaded files will only be used for editorial communication and publication purposes.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 60px;">Nahor will not share personal information with third parties without consent.</p>
    
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
